&lt;li&gt;Own strategic account planning and executive engagement for top platforms in the portfolio: define multi‑quarter account roadmaps, support executive business reviews, and ensure broad sponsorship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set clear goals focused on product distribution that tie directly to business impact. Measure and report on performance metrics at an executive level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and scale programmatic account management processes: implement repeatable adoption, churn-risk, optimization, and renewal playbooks that balance scalability with bespoke engagement for strategic accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate cross‑functional delivery and escalation management in support of annual growth initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own account health, volume forecasting, and growth goals; align Stripe and customer leadership on success metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
